---
title: Sweet ’n’ Spicy Apricot Chicken with Broccoli & Garlic Cauliflower Rice
description: This chicken dinner is a little bit sweet, a little bit spicy, and all around tasty! Juicy chicken cutlets are drizzled with a tangy sauce of apricot jam, ponzu sauce, Sriracha, and butter. On the side, there’s fluffy, aromatic garlic rice, plus tender roasted broccoli. Fruity flavor with a dash of heat? This combo can’t be beat!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-n-spicy-apricot-chicken-81203979.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/646e35a404f29d9817049e8f.pdf
cuisine: Asian
time required: 25 minutes
course: main course
